/avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"There is a new quota for managed policies:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\niam:quota-policynumber\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nand a new cloud property for configuration of the attachment limit:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# euctl authentication.max_policy_attachments\r\nauthentication.max_policy_attachments = 10\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# euctl -d authentication.max_policy_attachments\r\nauthentication.max_policy_attachments = 10\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# euctl -s authentication.max_policy_attachments\r\nauthentication.max_policy_attachments = Maximum number of attached managed policies\r\n#\r\n#\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nLimits for attachments and policy size are now included in the output from GetAccountSummary:\r\n\r\n* AttachedPoliciesPerGroupQuota\r\n* AttachedPoliciesPerRoleQuota\r\n* AttachedPoliciesPerUserQuota\r\n* PolicySizeQuota\r\n\r\nError responses for iam managed policy actions are updated to match the error codes and http status codes used by aws/iam.\r\n\r\nThe following n4j pull request is updated with tests covering functionality for this story.\r\n\r\n  https://github.com/eucalyptus/n4j/pull/41","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atla